description: CpriLinkSupervision: Table recording CPRI link supervision data for each cell, including timestamps, location, cell identifiers, and supervision parameters.  dateTime: Timestamp of the record; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Arbitrary identifier; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; CpriLinkFilterTime:  CPRI link filter time; CpriLinkSupervision.cpriLinkSupervisionId:  Unique identifier for this specific supervision record.
